Event.EventArg: …After God left, the world was thrown into chaos.
To bring order to this chaos, the Spirit Kingdom was founded.
The Spirit Prince, Princess, and others unified the Earth in harmony.
But after eight thousand years, even an immortal spirit will become
The rulers of each spirit family were tasked with leading their own.
Being so different, they could not share the world.
Thus, they battled with one another for ultimate supremacy.
Corpses filled the valleys, and the rivers ran red with blood.
When God did not return, Spirit Demea offered herself as a sacrifice.
With this ritual, she entered the horizon between Heaven and Earth.
There, she felt just a faint glimmer, a sign of God's presence.
But instead of a Second Coming, all that came was an outpouring
A shadow was cast over the world, and dark beings invaded the Earth.
The spirits fought against these beings of darkness.
They sealed them within the great fiery abyss in the center
But some of them escaped before they could be sealed.
Injured, they hid themselves away to rest in remote places.
The depths of the forests, the mountain peaks, the edges of clouds…
Fascinated with the darkness, Spirit Baalveil and his kin soon left
